--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scope of this licence and the per-tree licences
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This LICENSE covers the content of THIS (umbrella / orchestration) repository:
the build-log, change record, documentation, scripts, tests, installer sources
and packaging orchestration authored by Bastion Software Solutions Ltd, together
with the retained upstream copyrights above.

The Bastion Krypton Suite is a DUAL-LICENCE project spread across four
repositories. The source trees carry their OWN, unchanged upstream licences,
which govern the code in those trees:

  * Standard-Toolkit (core five libraries) ...... BSD 3-Clause
        (c) Component Factory Pty Ltd; (c) Krypton Suite
        -> Standard-Toolkit/LICENSE

  * Standard-Toolkit-Demos (samples) ............ BSD 3-Clause
        (c) Krypton Suite
        -> Standard-Toolkit-Demos/LICENSE

  * Extended-Toolkit (Extended modules) ......... MIT
        (c) 2017 - 2024 Krypton Suite
        -> Extended-Toolkit/LICENSE
        Several Extended modules embed third-party code under MIT / Ms-PL and
        (historically) other licences; see Extended-Toolkit/THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md
        and docs/audit/THIRD-PARTY-LICENCES.md.

Redistributed BINARIES/PACKAGES carry the licence of the tree they derive from:
core NuGet packages are BSD-3-Clause; Extended packages are MIT (or "MIT AND
MS-PL" for the Ms-PL-bundling modules and the Extended Ultimate metapackage). No
package blends the two licences in one artefact.

Upstream copyright and licence headers are retained unchanged throughout. This
project is NOT affiliated with or endorsed by Component Factory Pty Ltd or the
Krypton Suite team; the name "Bastion Krypton Suite" states its derivation
honestly under the terms of the upstream BSD-3-Clause and MIT licences.

Full attribution and the change record: CHANGES.md.
